## Installation
```bash
pip install bbm
```

## Example
```python
from bbm import Interval, logging, setup


@logging()
def temp_func():
    return "Hello World"


@logging(process_name="custom_name_of_process", interval=Interval.A_DAY)
def temp_func2():
    return "Hello World"


if __name__ == "__main__":
    setup(es_url="your-es-url", index_prefix="your-index-prefix")
    temp_func()
    temp_func2()
```
